 The Weeknd 打破温布利球场门票销售纪录https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-breaks-wembley-stadium-ticket-sales-record-3486018?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-weeknd-breaks-wembley-stadium-ticket-销售记录Liberty DunworthMon, 21 Aug 2023 12:29:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3486018 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="周末" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位创作歌手今年早些时候还打破了伦敦体育场最高上座率记录</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-breaks-wembley-stadium-ticket-sales-record-3486018">《The Weeknd》打破温布利球场门票销售记录的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="周末" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/the-weeknd-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd</a>在伦敦的演出打破了另一项记录——这次是温布利球场的门票销售量记录。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-weeknd-live-in-manchester-setlist-photos-3454668">曼彻斯特 The Weeknd 现场直播：夏季最新大片</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwGo2cgo5lj/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Live Nation UK</em></a>首先强调了这一消息，该公司宣布这位多次获得格莱美奖的艺术家“打破了温布利体育场传统音乐会布置的销售记录”。</p><p>报道还称，他这么做是因为周五（8 月 18 日）举行的伦敦演出“售出了 87,000 张门票”。这次约会是他正在进行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-adds-wembley-stadium-date-to-after-hours-til-dawn-tour-3366891">“After Hours &#39;Til Dawn”巡回演唱会</a>的一部分，也是欧洲站的最后一次约会。</p><p>上周 Live Nation 宣布了这一纪录后，这位真名是 Abel Tesfaye 的艺术家在他现已过期的 Instagram 故事中分享了这一成就。他的 XO 唱片公司联合创始人 Cash 也分享了这一更新，他写道：“恭喜我的兄弟@theweeknd wowowowow。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwGo2cgo5lj/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;